Alhaji Isa Funtua, a close ally of President Muhammadu Buhari, is dead Funtua reportedly died on Monday after suffering cardiac arrest. Buhari’s spokesmen, Bashir Ahmed confirmed the development on Twitter He wrote, “Inna lillahi wa inna ilaihi raji’un! Just heard about Mallam Ismaila Isa Funtua’s sudden death. “This life! May Allah accept his soul, forgive his shortcomings and grant him Jannah al-Firdaus.”